  "description": {
    "zh": "我一直是 SCAR 步枪的忠实粉丝，我的很多手下都用这款枪，实在是太棒了。不过我不是为了夸它才来找你，我有个小请求。\n\n我需要两把 MK17，一黑一沙色。\n\n黑色那把要配 Razor 望远镜和 RMR 红点（最好是装在瞄镜上），还能折叠，装上两脚架、消音器和战术装置。\n\n沙色那把则需要装 Lantac BMD 消焰器、MAWL 激光和 BOSS Xe 光学瞄具。两把枪都至少得装 20 发。你能搞定吗？\n\nBlack SCAR-H 要求：\n - 后坐力总和小于 450\n - 重量小于 5.5 公斤\n - 人机功效 30 或更高\n - 耐久度至少 95 %\n - 弹匣容量 20 或更多\n - 宽度占用 6格 或更少\n - 任意 消音器\n - 任意 战术设备\n - 任意 脚架\n - Trijicon RMR\n - Vortex Razor HD Gen.2 1-6x24步枪瞄准镜\n\nFDE SCAR-H 要求：\n - 后坐力总和小于 330\n - 重量小于 4.0 公斤\n - 人机功效 69 或更高\n - 耐久度至少 95 %\n - 弹匣容量 20 或更多\n - MAWL-C1+战术装置\n - Lantac“爆炸缓冲装置” 7.62x51\n - Wilcox BOSS Xe反射式瞄具",
    "en": "I am a huge fan of SCAR rifles, most of my guys carry them, great rifles. But I didn't contact you just to tell you that, I have a small request, I need two MK17 rifles, one in black, one in tan.\n\nLet's get the specifics out of the way, the black MK17 should have a Razor scope and a RMR reflex sight, preferably mounted on the scope if possible, it should be foldable and be equipped with a bipod, suppressor and have a tactical device.\n\nThe tan MK17 needs a Lantac BMD, a MAWL laser and a BOSS Xe optic. Both weapons should hold at least twenty rounds in the magazine. Can you help out here?\n\nBlack SCAR-H Requirements :\n - Recoil Sum less than 450\n - Weight less than 5.5 KG\n - Ergonomics 30 or higher\n - Durability higher than 95 %\n - Magazine Capacity of 20 or more\n - Width of 6 slots or less\n - A Silencer\n - A Tactical Device\n - A Bipod\n - Trijicon RMR Reflex Sight\n - Vortex Razor HD Gen.2 1-6x24 30mm Riflescope\n\nFDE SCAR-H Requirements :\n - Recoil Sum less than 330\n - Weight less than 4.0 KG\n - Ergonomics 69 or higher\n - Durability higher than 95 %\n - Magazine Capacity of 20 or more\n - B.E. Meyers MAWL-C1+ Tactical Device\n - Lantac BMD 7.62x51 Blast Mitigation Device\n - Wilcox BOSS Xe Reflex Sight"
  },
